        "metadata": {
          "description": "Kleisli composition for optionals.",
          "comments": [
            "compose(f, g, x) returns the Kleisli composition of f and g applied to x: bind(f(x), g).",
            "If either f or the second stage produces none, the result is none.",
            "Total. Corresponds to Haskell's Kleisli composition for Maybe, (>=>) :: (a -> Maybe b) -> (b -> Maybe c) -> a -> Maybe c."],
          "seeAlso": []},
        "signature": {
          "typeParameters": [{"name": "x", "constraints": []}, {"name": "y", "constraints": []}, {"name": "z", "constraints": []}],
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "f",
              "description": "the first Kleisli arrow",
              "type": {"function": {"domain": {"variable": "x"}, "codomain": {"optional": {"variable": "y"}}}},
              "isLazy": false},
            {
              "name": "g",
              "description": "the second Kleisli arrow",
              "type": {"function": {"domain": {"variable": "y"}, "codomain": {"optional": {"variable": "z"}}}},
              "isLazy": false},
            {"name": "x", "description": "the value to apply the composition to", "type": {"variable": "x"}, "isLazy": false}],
          "result": {"type": {"optional": {"variable": "z"}}}},
        "isPure": true,
        "isTotal": true,
        "defaultImplementation": {
          "lambda": {
            "parameter": "f",
            "body": {
              "lambda": {
                "parameter": "g",
                "body": {
                  "lambda": {
                    "parameter": "x",
                    "body": {
                      "application": {
                        "function": {
                          "application": {
                            "function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.optionals.bind"},
                            "argument": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "f"}, "argument": {"variable": "x"}}}}},
                        "argument": {"variable": "g"}}}}}}}}}}},
    {
      "primitive": {
        "name": "hydra.lib.optionals.foldList",
        "metadata": {
          "description": "Left-fold over a list with an optional-returning function, short-circuiting on none.",
          "comments": [
            "foldList(f, acc, xs) folds f over xs from the left, iterating while each application yields given, and returns none as soon as any step yields none. If every element is processed, the result is given of the final accumulator.",
            "foldList(f, acc, xs) is lists.foldl(\\m y -> bind(m, \\x -> f(x, y)), pure(acc), xs); this defining equation is the specification, and the default implementation.",
            "Total. Corresponds to a short-circuiting foldM specialised to Maybe."],
          "seeAlso": []},
        "signature": {
          "typeParameters": [{"name": "x", "constraints": []}, {"name": "y", "constraints": []}],
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "f",
              "description": "the optional-returning step function",
              "type": {
                "function": {
                  "domain": {"variable": "x"},
                  "codomain": {"function": {"domain": {"variable": "y"}, "codomain": {"optional": {"variable": "x"}}}}}},
              "isLazy": false},
            {"name": "acc", "description": "the initial accumulator", "type": {"variable": "x"}, "isLazy": false},
            {"name": "xs", "description": "the list to fold over", "type": {"list": {"variable": "y"}}, "isLazy": false}],
          "result": {"type": {"optional": {"variable": "x"}}}},
        "isPure": true,
        "isTotal": true,
        "defaultImplementation": {
          "lambda": {
            "parameter": "f",
            "body": {
              "lambda": {
                "parameter": "acc",
                "body": {
                  "lambda": {
                    "parameter": "xs",
                    "body": {
                      "application": {
                        "function": {
                          "application": {
                            "function": {
                              "application": {
                                "function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.lists.foldl"},
                                "argument": {
                                  "lambda": {
                                    "parameter": "m",
                                    "body": {
                                      "lambda": {
                                        "parameter": "y",
                                        "body": {
                                          "application": {
                                            "function": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.optionals.bind"}, "argument": {"variable": "m"}}},
                                            "argument": {
                                              "lambda": {
                                                "parameter": "x",
                                                "body": {
                                                  "application": {
                                                    "function": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "f"}, "argument": {"variable": "x"}}},
                                                    "argument": {"variable": "y"}}}}}}}}}}}}},
                            "argument": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.optionals.pure"}, "argument": {"variable": "acc"}}}}},
                        "argument": {"variable": "xs"}}}}}}}}}}},
